text: Thomas James Hockenson (born July 3, 1997) is an American football tight end for the Minnesota Vikings of the National Football League (NFL). He was drafted in the first round of the 2019 NFL Draft by the Detroit Lions. He played college football at the University of Iowa. ==Other websites== *Detroit Lions bio *Iowa Hawkeyes bio Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:American football tight ends Category:Detroit Lions players Category:Minnesota Vikings players
